content.raw: Looks good to me but we should verify that the code snippets work as expected when the pull request is merged. I cannot visualize it locally because the `include` references a file that is not merged yet.

content.raw: I made some style updates. The other issue is related with the `<include>` blocks. I believe you are using `from` and `to` specifying line numbers. I might be wrong but I think that the value has to be a regexp.

content.raw: Use `/atlas/atlas_sim_interface_command`, otherwise the character *_* makes the word to look funny.
